# Implementation Plan - Crypto Transfer Configuration

Enable administrators to configure a Crypto Wallet for receiving manual payments.

## User Review Required
> [!NOTE]
> I will add a "Crypto Transfer Configuration" section to the Admin Dashboard. This will be for *manual* text display to users (instructional), not an automated crypto gateway (unless specified otherwise).

